           int hidden_neurons,
           ELMFunction activation_function,
           int classes,
           AbstractMoorePenroseMethod inverse,
           int maxEvaluations)
        Construct an ELM
        Parameters:
        elm_type - Elm type - classification or regression
        hidden_neurons - Number of hidden neurons assigned to the ELM
        activation_function - Type of activation function - Type of activation function: 'sig' for Sigmoidal function 'sin' for Sine function 'hardlim' for Hardlim function 'tribas' for Triangular basis function 'radbas' for Radial basis function
        classes - number of classes
        inverse - Method for calculation of moore penrose inverse
        maxEvaluations - Maximun number of evaluations
